 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x10d5",
   "jp_len": 45,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "あいうえおかダチッツテ{01}タ{00}·{00}！ア{00}MュMな、{00}{01}！し{00}MせIな、{00}{01}ぁ好了…",
   "zh_hex": "15161718191a1b65666768690164000400064e00137f13330200010623001327123302000115e7c7e7ba090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1102",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、首先就让我、来见识见识你们的本{00}事吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef40ef8be7c5e7f9efcc02efcfe85ce92fe85ce92fe7b8e7bbe7b4efa600efb8e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x114a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、先让你们和这些家伙、过过招吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02b8e7f9e7b8e7bbe7d3e7b9e8a4e7dfe7fd02ef36ef36e97ae7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x115f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对付几台自动操纵的无人机、应该不在话{00}下吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee97eeaa5ea16efb5ef30eac7e8e6e7b4e7dcefb2e7e402e873e898e7b5ef29e81f00ef4de7d005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x119d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "了解",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bae89d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11a4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、阿波利、罗伯托！先由你们来{00}示范一下",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7d2e9a8e82e02e7eceaa4e7f406b8e8a6e7b8e7bbd900eab0ec8e87890000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11e7",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白、大佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e80902efa5efbaef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1217",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、先来复习一遍刚才战斗里的示范吧{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef8befcfe9eeeab6efb6edbfe8bce836ef28e7ffef31e7b4eab0ec8ee7d000ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1238",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、是关于『小队』！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40ef8b02e7b6e8bbe8790ce83ee7c90def9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1276",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "像这样、多个单位处在同一格里的状态、{00}就叫『小队』！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e9e7b9e7da02e7e9e828e918e834e903ef29e85defb6e824ef31e7b4e98be9940200e7c5e8c10ce83ee7c90def970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12b8",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}关于小队",
   "zh_hex": "1501010101e8bbe879e83ee7c90000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12c7",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把多个单位、配置在同一格里的状态、称{00}为『小队』",
   "zh_hex": "15e81be7e9e828e918e83402ea34ea0eef29e85defb6e824ef31e7b4e98be99402ea0100e7c10ce83ee7c90d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12e8",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『小队』最多由3台组成、队内单位、可{00}同时行动和战斗",
   "zh_hex": "150ce83ee7c90de8c5e7e9e8a6ef60ea16ea0de83702e7c9e99ae918e83402e7c400e85def2defd6ef30e7d3ef28e7ff000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x130d",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、选择『小队攻击』、还能对敌方全{00}体、发动攻击",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e966eaaa0ce83ee7c9ef67e7cc0d02e7f7e7c6e7bee7e3efb1efb400ef4f02e870ef30ef67e7cc00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1355",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要这样、一场战斗里、就能让多台机体{00}一同上阵！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7b9e7da02efb6e876ef28e7ffef3102e7c5e7c6e7f9e7e9ea16e7e4ef4f00efb6e85def4ceb48ef97ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1371",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听好了、看清楚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7c7e7ba02e7f6e995ebd30909ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13a3",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战斗、基本上就是靠这个『小队』来进行{00}的",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ff02e829efa6ef4ce7c5e7b6e8c7e7b9e8280ce83ee7c90defcfe892efd600e7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13dc",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、接下来是攻击的方法……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efceef4defcfe7b6ef67e7cce7b4efb1e84e090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13ec",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是『近接』和『射击』、这两者的区{00}别！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b60cefd8efce0de7d30cef65e7cc0d02e7b9e97def6ee7b4ef3500e7e5ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1424",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}近接射击区别",
   "zh_hex": "15010196b7ace7ccef35e7e5000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1436",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『近接』没有弹数限制、命中率也高、但{00}出手会慢一些",
   "zh_hex": "150cefd8efce0de7d8e7cbe946e914eb23e8de02e853ef4ee9e1e7c0e81202e7db00efbeef66e7e2e979efb6e8a4000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x145b",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "即便抢先出手、若对方选了『射击』、也{00}会反被对方抢先命中",
   "zh_hex": "15e855e8faebc8ef8befbeef6602e7e7e7beefb1e966e7ba0cef65e7cc0d02e7c000e7e2e87ce7f1e7beefb1ebc8ef8be853ef4e00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1482",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另一方面、『射击』出手快、威力也高、{00}但弹数有限",
   "zh_hex": "15e99befb6efb1e862020cef65e7cc0defbeef66e85f02e96befb0e7c0e8120200e7dbe946e914e7cbeb230000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14c6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战斗的基础、大致就是这些了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ffe7b4e829eb9602efa5ea32e7c5e7b6e7b9e8a4e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14d5",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "剩下的、就让你们实际打一场、亲自确认{00}确认吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea3aef4de7b402e7c5e7f9e7b8e7bbe87fedc3e7f5efb6e87602e894efb5e88ce8a000e88ce8a0e7d0ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1516",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就看你身手了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7f6e7b8e88def66e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1528",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这家伙只会用『近接』攻击、好好利用这{00}一点、把它打倒吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dfe7fdef32e7e2d80c96b70d9ee7cc02e7c7e7c7e82ed8e7b90087e82202e81be978e7f5e848e7d006000000000000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1574",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是这里！上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e7b9ef31ef97ef4cef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15d4",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才、扎古选的就是『近接』",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce83602e84be84de966e7b4e7c5e7b60cefd8efce0d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15f0",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "命中率和暴击率都高、而且能无限次使用{00}、这是它的特点",
   "zh_hex": "15e853ef4ee9e1e7d3ea4fe7cce9e1e840e81202e89ce999e7c6e7dceb23e864e83fefb30002e7b9e7b6e978e7b4e7cfe822000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x161d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x164c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "缺点是、一旦对方选了『射击』、就会被{00}对方抢先攻击！",
   "zh_hex": "15ee81e822e7b602efb6ebcde7beefb1e966e7ba0cef65e7cc0d02e7c5e7e2e7f100e7beefb1ebc8ef8bef67e7ccef970000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1696",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就像这样、『射击』会先一步命中",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e8e9e7b9e7da020cef65e7cc0de7e2ef8befb6ea93e853ef4e000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16e8",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是那样的！再给我重来一次！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6e7b7e7dae7b4ef97e80be839efcce8a1efcfefb6e864ef97ef97000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1726",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此、看来基础部分、你们掌握得相{00}当扎实嘛",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca02e7f6efcfe829eb96ef70efae02e7b8e7bbeb36eb37e80ae8b100ef53e84be87fe93600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1740",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、战斗里、可不全是能让你轻松取胜{00}的对手哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602ef28e7ffef3102e7c4e7b5efb4e7b6e7c6e7f9e7b8e990e9e0e987e8db00e7b4e7beef66e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1785",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比方说、这家伙的装甲和火力、都在扎古{00}之上……",
   "zh_hex": "15e825d0e7ed02e7b9e7dfe7fde7b4e98febdbe7d3e8dada02e840ef29e84be84d00e7cdb209090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17a0",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而且、驾驶它的、也不是什么AI、而是{00}海兵队的好手",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce99902e953e975e978e7b402e7c0e7b5e7b6e7dde7bdea9cef6202e89ce7b600e91bef93e7c9e7b4e7c7ef66000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17bd",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、面对这样的对手、你们打算怎么打{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e862e7bee7b9e7dae7b4e7beef6602e7b8e7bbe7f5e889e7f2e7bde7f5000500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17f4",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对付那样的对手、『ID指令』就很有效{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee97ee7b7e7dae7b4e7beef66020cef62ef96e8c0e94e0de7c5e981e7cbea8f00e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x182b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}ID指令",
   "zh_hex": "15010101011211e8c0e94e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1838",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "每个角色、都拥有一种名为『ID指令』{00}的特殊能力",
   "zh_hex": "15ec25e828eb1ae89f02e840eb35e7cb87e7d1e8ace7c10c1211e8c0e94e0d00e7b4e7cfed7be7c6da00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x185a",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在战斗中、通过使用这个『ID指令』、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29ef28e7ffef4e02ef59ef36e83fefb3e7b9e8280cef62ef96e8c0e94e0d020000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1875",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就能获得诸如、造成更多伤害之类的效果",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7c6e9d8e80aea56e7f002e93ee837e952e7e9e8f9e988e7cde841e7b4ea8fe87100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18b9",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么阿波利、就由你来示范给大家看看吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bde7d2e9a8e82e02e7c5e8a6e7b8d9eab0ec8ee839bee7dfe7f6e7f6e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18e8",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e809ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1915",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我所拥有的『ID指令』、有这么几{00}个……",
   "zh_hex": "158be7fbeb35e7cbe7b40c1211e8c0e94e0d02e7cbe7b9e7bdeaa500e82809090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1946",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就是这些！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e7b6e7b9e8a4ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1951",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "其中……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cfef4e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x195a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这个『……行吗！？』、有着提升伤害{00}和命中的效果！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e8280c09099fe80206050d02e7cbe86de821ed2be8f9e98800e7d3e853c0e7b4ea8fe871060000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19a0",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、先用它、把那台MS给打倒吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02ef8befb3e97802e81be7b7ea16efa7ef9ee839e7f5e848e7d0ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19dd",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在武器选择画面上、把光标移到『ID指{00}令』并确定后……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e8ece8c3e966eaaaecefe862ef4c02e81be83de96fec83e7d70cef62ef96e8c000e94e0de957e88ce867e7fe090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19fd",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就会进入这个『ID指令选择画面』",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7e2e892e891e7b9e8280cef62ef96e8c0e94ee966eaaaecefe8620d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a0f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在这里、选好想用的『ID指令』、再按{00}『确定』！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9ef3102e966e7c7e7e6efb3e7b40cef62ef96e8c0e94e0d02e80bea76000ce88ce8670def970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a44",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "像这样活用『ID指令』、对上强敌、也{00}能把战局往有利的方向推进",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e9e7b9e7dae8d4d80c1211e8c0e94e0d02e7beb2e8ade7e302e7c000e7c6e81bef28ea8ce911e7cbe82ee7b4d09deaabe892000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a67",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、有一点、是必须得注意的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e7cbefb6e82202e7b6e860e9a2e80aeaccef3ce7b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a81",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是、使用『ID指令』、是需要花{00}费『SP』的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b602e83fd80c1211e8c0e94e0d02e7b6e92def2aeb9f00e95d0c14eed40de7b400000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac3",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}关于SP",
   "zh_hex": "1501010101e8bbe879ef9eeed40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ad2",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "每个角色、都拥有一个代表精神力的、名{00}为『SP』的数值",
   "zh_hex": "15ec25e828eb1ae89f02e840eb35e7cb87e828e8e7e9e7e98de9aadae7b402e8ac00e7c10c14eed40de7b4e914ec48000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af5",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "每当使用『ID指令』时、",
   "zh_hex": "15ec25ef53e83fefb30cef62ef96e8c0e94e0def2d0200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b04",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就会花费掉、各个指令所规定的『SP』",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7e2eb9fe95de9d302e819e828e8c0e94ee7fbea42e867e7b40c14eed40d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b1c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "指令越是强力、所花费的『SP』、也就{00}越多",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c0e94eea57e7b6e8adda02e7fbeb9fe95de7b40c14eed40d02e7c0e7c500ea57e7e90000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b37",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}{01}SP增减",
   "zh_hex": "150101010101ef9eeed4ea3ded24000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b48",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "每个角色、都拥有一个名为『初始SP{00}值』的数值、",
   "zh_hex": "15ec25e828eb1ae89f02e840eb35e7cb87e828e8ace7c10ceb4fe90814eed400ec480de7b4e914ec4802000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b69",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "它就是关卡开始时、所持有的『SP』",
   "zh_hex": "15e978e7c5e7b6e8bbe801e7fae908ef2d02e7fbe9efe7cbe7b40cef9eeed40d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b84",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在那之后、随着回合推进、『SP』每回{00}合都会上升一定的数值",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b7e7cde7fe02e9a1e86d8ca0eaabe892020c14eed40dec258c00a0e840e7e2b2ed2b87e867e7b4e914ec480000000000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ba8",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、击破敌人、或是触发特定事件、也{00}会让它上升",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7ccef6de7e3efb202e905e7b6ef48e870e7cfe867efb8e99102e7c000e7e2e7f9e978ef4ced2b000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be6",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "关卡刚开始时、『SP』也少、用不了强{00}力的指令……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bbe801e8bce7fae908ef2d020cef9eeed40de7c0efac02efb3e7b5e7bae8ad00efb0e7b4e8c0e94e0909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c07",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但只要靠回合推进、或多击坠敌人、把{00}『SP』积累起来、",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbef32ef2ae8c78ca0eaabe89202e905e7e9e7cceb53e7e3b402e81b000c14eed40ded99ec33e847d9020000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c27",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就能使用那些强力的『ID指令』了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7c6e83fefb3e7b7e8a4e8adefb0e7b40cef62ef96e8c0e94e0de7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c43",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是从开局就勤用那些效果小的指令、",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e88ae7faea8ce7c5ed29efb3e7b7e8a4ea8fe871e83ee7b4e8c0e94e02000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5e",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还是花时间把『SP』积累起来、用强力{00}指令一举定胜负……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7b6eb9fef2de8fce81b0cef9eeed40ded99ec33e847efcf02efb3e8adefb000e8c0e94eefb6ea21e867e8dbe92c09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c81",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如何调控『SP』、是战斗中、十分重要{00}的一环",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efbce95cea3f0cef9eeed40d02e7b6ef28e7ffef4e02ea4aefaee8a1ef2a00e7b4efb6ef4700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ca5",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就来实地演练一下、运用『ID指{00}令』的战斗吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5efcfe87fef63ea2feb13efb6ef4d02e986efb30cef62ef96e8c000e94e0de7b4ef28e7ffe7d0000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ced",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人、是两台强力的MS……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb202e7b6e97dea16e8adefb0e7b4efa7ef9e0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cfc",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "活用『小队』和『ID指令』、把它们击{00}破",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d4efb30ce83ee7c90de7d30cef62ef96e8c0e94e0d02e81be978e7bbe7cc00ef6d00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d17",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿波利、罗伯托、给西玛中佐、露一手你{00}们的本事！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e9a8e82e02e7eceaa4e7f402e839e7f8e845c0a302e85887aee7b800e7bbe7b4d2a9060000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d59",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这家伙……能行吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dfe7fd0909e7c6efd6e802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d8f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上啊——！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef4ce7c3ebafebafef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dc0",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……怎么了？阿波利、罗伯托？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7f2e7bde7ba05e7d2e9a8e82e02e7eceaa4e7f405000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dec",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对、对不起、大佐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7be02e7bee7b5e84702efa5efba09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e16",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请再让我们来一次！这一次、一定……",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae80be7f9efcce7bbefcfefb6e864ef97e7b9efb6e86402efb6e86709090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e48",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的、拿你们没办法……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b402e9a7e7b8e7bbe7d8e8eae84e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e55",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就再给你们一次机会吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e80be839e7b8e7bbefb6e864e7e4e7e2e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e91",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么样、西玛中佐？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7da02e7f8e845ef4eefba0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e9d",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们的实力、您应该已经有所了解了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4e87fefb002e835e873e898ef3ae8b7e7cbe7fbe7bae89de7bae7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1edd",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光凭这点程度、还不足以让我、把后背交{00}托给你们呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e83dea49e7b9e822ea7de96d02e7f7e7b5ea1ee7f3e7f9efcc02e81be7fee9e4e86100e7f4e839e7b8e7bbe90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ef9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战斗里、可还有着、各种各样的要素呢",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ffef3102e7c4e7f7e7cbe86d02e819e7d1e819e7dae7b4ef2aec86e90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f10",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们要怎么去应对那些、也得让我好好瞧{00}瞧才行……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbef2ae7f2e7bde7ebe873e7bee7b7e8a402e7c0e80ae7f9efcce7c7e7c7ead400ead4e836efd6090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f4c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就先稍作休整、然后继续演习吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5ef8bead5ef2fe90ee9fe02e7efe7fee9d6e9adea2feab6e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6b",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西玛中佐、这样、可以吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e845ef4eefba02e7b9e7da02e7c4e7f3e7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f96",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊啊、没问题",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7c302e7d8e997ea120000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fc7",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚大佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6efa5efbaef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fcf",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西玛中佐传来联络、说差不多想重启演习{00}了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e845ef4eefbaea38efcfef2eeb1402e7ede9c7e7b5e7e9e7e6e8a1ea3bea2feab600e7baef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2009",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2011",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我们这边也得、把出击的部队『编{00}成』好才行",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7bbe7b9e899e7c0e80a02e81befbee7cce7b4ef70e7c90cec8900e8370de7c7e836efd60000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2063",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{01}{01}{01}{01}{01}编成",
   "zh_hex": "150101010101ec89e8370000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2072",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要让单位在关卡中出击、必须事先进行{00}『编成』",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7f9e918e834ef29e8bbe801ef4eefbee7cc02e860e9a2efb8ef8be892efd6000cec89e8370d00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2095",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在后台菜单中、选择『编成』之后……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7feea16eeade918c002e966eaaa0cec89e8370de7cde7fe0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ae",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就会切换到这个『编成』画面",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7e2ef3fea78e7d7e7b9e8280cec89e8370decefe8620000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20bf",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在这里、把想出击的单位、搭载到战舰上{00}、并为其配属驾驶员",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9ef3102e81be7e6efbee7cce7b4e918e83402eb09eb1de7d7ef28e7d4ef4c0002e957e7c1e8cfea34ea24e953e975e84900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20de",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『编成』完成后、接下来、就是实际的{00}『出击』了",
   "zh_hex": "150cec89e8370de87ee837e7fe02efceef4defcf02e7c5e7b6e87fedc3e7b4000cefbee7cc0de7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20fa",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在后台的『作战』中、选择『进击』之后{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7feea16e7b40cef2fef280def4e02e966eaaa0ce892e7cc0de7cde7fe000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2116",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就会切换到这个『出击』画面",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7e2ef3fea78e7d7e7b9e8280cefbee7cc0decefe862000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2127",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在这里、按下『A键』、便会进入下一关",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9ef3102ea76ef4d0cea9ceb710d02e8fae7e2e892e891ef4defb6e8bb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x215b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "母舰已经准备好了、",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d5e7d4ef3ae8b7e87ae877e7c7e7ba02000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2170",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "剩下、就请把机体和驾驶员、编入战舰里{00}吧",
   "zh_hex": "15ea3aef4d02e7c5e83ae81be7e4ef4fe7d3e953e975e84902ec89e891ef28e7d4ef3100e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21a1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "了解了、玛利根",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bae89de7ba02e845e82ee9b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d96",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5da3",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你陪『宇宙世纪路线』一路走到了最{00}后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8ef420ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2e890e7d7e7bae8c500e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5dc3",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "隆德·贝尔队的战斗、就先在此告一段落{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a0009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5de2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请尽情享{00}受下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae8f2e88bec0600e8c8ef4de7eb000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e07",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为通关本路线的你、还准备了特别{00}关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7bae7cfe7e500e8bbe801000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e2e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头作战的大天使队之间的特{00}别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832efcce7bbefaee92eef2fef28e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cf00e7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e4f",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们一战、试试你亲手培养的部队有多{00}强、也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbefb6ef2802e91de91de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c9e7cbe7e900e8ad02e7c0e7b5e8850000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e74",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便能与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bbefb6ef28000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e99",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ebd",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也请慢慢地、尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e83ae979e979ef6302e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f36",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一直陪着我这么个不可靠的舰长走{00}到现在",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e7bde828e7b5e7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef34e89000e7d7e82fef29000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f55",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f73",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说我们预防者的战斗已经结束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7edefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895e7ba0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f8d",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过游戏本身还能继续、之后也请接{00}着尽情享受哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7f7e7c6e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83aefce00e86de8f2e88bec06e8c8e919000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fb3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我还为通关本路线的你、准备了一个新关{00}卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f7e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e87ae877e7baefb6e828ef8ae8bb00e801e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fd7",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是和我们分头、与提坦斯和新吉翁作战{00}的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7d38be7bbcde92e02e832e821e843e7c8e7d3ef8ae7d9ee88ef2fef2800e7b4090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ff2",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……隆德·贝尔队的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6005",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef28e9190000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x602b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请你务必去挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b8e94fe860e7ebeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6039",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x605d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲过去吧、大天使号{00}！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95eef36e7ebe7d002efa5e844e83fe83300ef97ef970d0000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60de",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60ee",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路出色的指挥致以{00}敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2afe89fe7b4e8c0e949ea32e7f300ee38ef3c00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6110",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的协助、我们才得以奋战到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7cbe7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3ef46ef28e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6132",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6148",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说我们主天使队的战斗已到此为止……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7edefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae7d7e7cae7c1e869090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6161",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请尽情享{00}受下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae8f2e88bec0600e8c8ef4de7eb0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6185",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战之后仍可继续、另外选择『特别{00}演习』、还能……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28e7cde7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e99be8f7e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e500ea2feab60d02e7f7e7c60909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61b0",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与隆德·贝尔、预防者展开一场联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee989e7faefb6e876ef2eefc0ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61ce",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以你的实力、与他们交手也一定{00}能取胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4e87fefb002e832e80ce7bbe861ef66e7c0efb6e86700e7c6e987e8db0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61f3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6217",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "往后也祝你武运长久、奋战不息",
   "zh_hex": "15e911e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db02ef46ef28e7b5ec6a000000"
  }
 ]
}
